<br>
Those who seek to slay all four of the warders and release this foul beast do the work of the minions of evil.  Death and destruction will surely follow this act and it may be wise for the guilds and clans that claim an allegiance to good to meet in a great Council to consider the ominous news that the foolhardy are considering such an act.<br>
<br>
The Band of Dreamers will gladly send a representative to such a meeting if others agree that we should act with common cause to stop the awakening of the Sleeper!<br>
<br>
Akida al`Takish, the Dreamer<br>
Fier`dal Druid of the 43rd rank<br>
Provisional Leader of the Band of Dreamers<br>
